{"data":[{"date":"14:52 13/07","title":"Barca chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua sao kh\u1ee7ng Chelsea n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/15/barca-chi-60-trieu-bang-mua-sao-khung-chelsea-nang-cap-tuyen-giua.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Kante c\u1ee7a Chelsea, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c The Blues nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Kante</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, vi\u1ec7c Iniesta sang Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 Paulinho tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Trung Qu\u1ed1c khi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd m\u1ecfng \u0111i \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. HLV Ernesto Valverde \u01b0u ti\u00ean vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve NGolo Kante\" title=\"tien ve NGolo Kante\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/6/thuc-hu-vu-psg-chi-100-trieu-euro-mua-kante.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua NGolo Kante</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nBarca mu\u1ed1n mua Kante c\u1ee7a Chelsea, HLV Valverde \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n The Blues chi \u0111\u1eadm cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKante \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, anh duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. Kante s\u1edf h\u1eefu n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c sung m\u00e3n c\u00f9ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111eo b\u00e1m d\u1ebbo dai.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 90 ph\u00fat m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi, anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e1n \u0111o\u00e1n. C\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Barca s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 Barca c\u00f3 Kante</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Chelsea b\u00e1n Kante, Barca ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, The Blues ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i t\u1eeb Leicester.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Kante c\u1ee7a Chelsea v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Kante c\u1ee7a Chelsea v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/19/Barca-muon-mua-Kante-cua-Chelsea-voi-gia-60-trieu-bang-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 Barca c\u00f3 Kante</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea s\u1ebd l\u00e3i l\u1edbn n\u1ebfu b\u00e1n Kante cho Barca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, song nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha. HLV Maurizio Sarri, ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1eafp ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Chelsea thay Conte mu\u1ed1n BL\u0110 The Blues gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n t\u1eeb Chelsea, Barca c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. Mirror cho r\u1eb1ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/thuc-hu-vu-psg-chi-100-trieu-euro-mua-kante-172-190952.html\" target=\"_blank\">PSG c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Kante</span>, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi t\u1edbi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i, Barca c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u0103ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p l\u00ean 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a TBN c\u00f2n ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn d\u00f9ng Andre Gomes \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c The Blues nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1222","checkdouble":"191104"},{"date":"15:18 13/07","title":"\u0110\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Man City b\u00eanh v\u1ef1c Sterling tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u00e3o ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/13/de-bruyne-phat-bieu-ve-sterling-dong-doi-tai-man-city.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kevin De Bruyne ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Sterling, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i Man City. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e0n em kh\u00f4ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch t\u1eeb d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn sau World Cup 2018.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Sterling m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ee9 7 n\u00e0y, khi B\u1ec9 g\u1eb7p Anh \u1edf tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng 3 World Cup 2018 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u00fac m\u00e0n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 th\u00fa v\u1ecb gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i Man City l\u00e0 Kevin De Bruyne v\u00e0 Raheem Sterling di\u1ec5n ra. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 De Bruyne t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o B\u1ec9 v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh th\u00ec Sterling l\u1ea1i g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u00e0n tr\u1ec1. Su\u1ed1t 5 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n sau 6 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i World Cup, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t 1 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ec3u l\u00e0 Panama.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"De Bruyne ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Sterling, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"De Bruyne ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Sterling, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/De-Bruyne-phat-bieu-ve-Sterling,-dong-doi-tai-Man-City-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">De Bruyne ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Sterling v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, Sterling th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean t\u1ecf ra v\u00f4 h\u1ea1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n. Trong nh\u1eefng pha x\u1eed l\u00fd, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh lu\u00f4n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 l\u00f3ng ng\u00f3ng v\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. Sau khi Tam s\u01b0 d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia, Sterling c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>De Bruyne b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng hay h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1ec1 Sterling, De Bruyne \u0111\u1ee9ng ra b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7. Anh tin r\u1eb1ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n em t\u1ea1i Man City kh\u00f4ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c \u0111\u00f3. &ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u t\u1ea1i sao h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u00e0o c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Sau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng l\u00e0m l\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng&rdquo;, De Bruyne ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Sterling.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y Sterling \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 t\u00f4i xem. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, khi b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n, t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c. Nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. Hy v\u1ecdng b\u00e1o ch\u00ed v\u00e0 gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00e0nh t\u00ecnh y\u00eau cho Sterling khi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c v\u00ec \u0110T Anh ngay c\u1ea3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-ly-do-khien-tam-su-khong-the-di-den-tran-dau-cuoi-cung-421-191024.html\">4 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Tam S\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/that-bai-cua-dt-anh-tai-world-cup-2018-chi-la-bong-da-chua-the-tro-ve-466-191001.html\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018: Ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/its-coming-home-niem-hy-vong-su-lo-bich-va-mong-ba-vuong-cua-tuyen-anh-421-190798.html\">&ldquo;It&rsquo;s Coming Home&rdquo; &ndash; Ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng, s\u1ef1 l\u1ed1 b\u1ecbch v\u00e0 m\u1ed9ng b\u00e1 v\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/that-bai-cua-dt-anh-tai-world-cup-2018-chi-la-bong-da-chua-the-tro-ve-466-191001.html\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018: Ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1221","checkdouble":"191106"},{"date":"15:48 13/07","title":"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i tin \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/13/philipp-lahm-phat-bieu-ve-dt-duc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Maurizio Sarri t\u1edbi Chelsea thay Conte ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian, d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Andreas Christensen</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, Napoli l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t t\u1ee9 3 Serie A (sau Juventus v\u00e0 Roma), h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn 29 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 38 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 58 tu\u1ed5i lu\u00f4n \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng gi\u1eefa t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Maurizio Sarri t\u1edbi Chelsea thay Conte h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Maurizio Sarri t\u1edbi Chelsea thay Conte h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/HLV-Maurizio-Sarri-toi-Chelsea-thay-Conte-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Andreas Christensen nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Sarri tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Sarri c\u00f3 t\u01b0 duy b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 kh\u00e1 gi\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi Pep Guardiola, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n b\u00f3ng ngay t\u1eeb b\u00ean ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. \u1ede Napoli, Kalidou Koulibaly l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m vai tr\u00f2 n\u00e0y. Trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Senegal chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c c\u1ee7a anh l\u00ean t\u1edbi 95% \u1edf Serie A 2017/18.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede Stamford Bridge, trung v\u1ec7 Andreas Christensen c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Conte s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChristensen c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t, m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1996 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 93,4%, anh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 t\u1ea7m v\u00f3c t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i gi\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi Koulibaly. N\u1ebfu HLV Maurizio Sarri t\u1edbi Chelsea, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Christensen s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Manchester City</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man City l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean h\u1ecfi mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho c\u1ee7a Napoli, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad \u0111\u00e3 2 l\u1ea7n tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i. Theo \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00e0 35 v\u00e0 44 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, song \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu HLV Sarri d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea thay Conte h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu HLV Sarri d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea thay Conte h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-neu-HLV-Sarri-dan-dat-Chelsea-thay-Conte-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sarri gi\u00fap Chelsea mua Jorginho</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1eeda xanh th\u00e0nh Manchester g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb th\u1ee9 3 b\u1edfi Jorginho \u0111ang \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n Chelsea. B\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Anh \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f3 2 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Chelsea v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Man City trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Th\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1ee7 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0 Napoli y\u00eau c\u1ea7u, th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn The Blues theo ti\u1ebfng g\u1ecdi c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y c\u0169 Sarri.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea s\u1ebd c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 &ldquo;bom t\u1ea5n&rdquo; Jorginho c\u00f9ng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m ra m\u1eaft HLV Sarri. Theo ESPN, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London s\u1ebd ra m\u1eaft HLV Sarri v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Eden Hazard</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus, nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Real Madrid l\u00e0 t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf. Vi\u1ec7c Neymar v\u00e0 Mbappe c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn khi\u1ebfn Los Blancos d\u1ed3n to\u00e0n l\u1ef1c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Eden Hazard c\u1ee7a Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sarri muon bien Hazard thanh trung tam trong loi choi cua Chelsea\" title=\"Sarri mu\u1ed1n bi\u1ebfn Hazard th\u00e0nh trung t\u00e2m trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/ha.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sarri mu\u1ed1n bi\u1ebfn Hazard th\u00e0nh trung t\u00e2m trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00f4m nay, Daily Mail kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Real ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Hazard, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 27 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn NHM Chelsea lo l\u1eafng khi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 Real c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n. HLV Sarri d\u00f9 ch\u01b0a ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Chelsea song mu\u1ed1n BL\u0110 The Blues gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u1edf l\u1ea1i b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV 58 tu\u1ed5i d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea quanh Hazard, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 400.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Hazard \u1edf l\u1ea1i, t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a anh v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a The Blues \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng ch\u00fa \u00fd t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Antonio Conte</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Conte l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho Chelsea trong 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i qu\u00e1 t\u1ec7, theo \u0111\u00f3 m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u mang v\u1ec1 cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge \u00edt nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t danh hi\u1ec7u.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea thay conte sarri\" title=\"Chelsea thay conte sarri\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/John-Terry-phat-bieu-ve-Antonio-Conte-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Conte b\u1ecb Chelsea th\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7y cay \u0111\u1eafng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch m\u00e0 Conte \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 48 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu chung s\u1ed1 ph\u1eadn v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u HLV tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee7a Chelsea.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Chelsea gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a t\u1edbi, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-137-conte-da-bi-chelsea-sa-thai-421-191062.html\" target=\"_blank\">HLV Conte \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i</span>. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia th\u1ee9 9 m\u1ea5t vi\u1ec7c \u1edf Chelsea d\u01b0\u1edbi k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 Abramovich.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAn \u1ee7i l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi Conte l\u00e0 \u00f4ng s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec1n b\u00f9 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Chelsea. T\u00ednh c\u1ea3 c\u1ef1u HLV Juventus, The Blues \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec1n b\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho c\u00e1c HLV.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Ruben Loftus-Cheek</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 chi qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n trong 2 k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, b\u1edfi v\u1eady h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng mua s\u1eafm qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 HLV Sarri s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111ang c\u00f3 trong tay.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ruben Loftus-Cheek\" title=\"Ruben Loftus-Cheek\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/16/Thay-gi-sau-vu-tien-ve-Ross-Barkley-toi-Chelsea-hinh-anh-5.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ruben Loftus-Cheek \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Sarri s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i g\u1ecdi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, trong s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y Ruben Loftus-Cheek l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t. Ng\u00f4i sao 22 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Crystal Palace.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLoftus-Cheek th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0110T Anh, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1996 c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Gareth Southgate trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, n\u1ebfu Sarri c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Alvaro Morata</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Alvaro Morata \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb Real Madrid, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc nh\u1eefng g\u00ec anh th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. Ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cho Diego Costa \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Morata\" title=\"Morata\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/22/4-doi-bong-lon-san-sang-chi-60-trieu-euro-mua-bom-xit-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Morata s\u1eafp b\u1eadt b\u00e3i kh\u1ecfi Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i Morata ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 11 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1993 t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u cao nh\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh. C\u1ef1u sao Real li\u00ean t\u1ee5c d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, anh b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ngon \u0103n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00f2n tranh ch\u1ea5p r\u1ea5t k\u00e9m, ch\u00ednh m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Chelsea kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Sarri \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o nh\u01b0 Morata, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n Chelsea \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Dries Mertens c\u1ee7a Napoli ho\u1eb7c Gonzalo Higuain c\u1ee7a Juventus \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Conte t\u1ea1i v\u1ecb Morata c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao th\u00eam c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh, song khi m\u00e0 \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 48 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i c\u00f2n Sarri s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m, th\u1eddi gian c\u1ee7a Morata \u1edf Stamford Bridge ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n t\u00ednh b\u1eb1ng ng\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n*Squawka.com</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1220","checkdouble":"191107"},{"date":"14:54 13/07","title":"T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai G\u0110KT Gede s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c VFF \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/28/tuong-lai-gdkt-gede-sap-duoc-vff-dinh-doat.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin, L\u0110B\u0110 Vi\u1ec7t Nam VFF s\u1ebd gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi G\u0110KT ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c, Jurgen Gede theo b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 2 n\u0103m.</h2><h2>VFF gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi G\u0110KT Jurgen Gede</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai G\u0110KT Jurgen Gede s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c VFF \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai G\u0110KT Jurgen Gede s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c VFF \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/19/Tuong-lai-GDKT-Jurgen-Gede-sap-duoc-VFF-dinh-doat-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>G\u0110KT Jurgen Gede s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u0110B\u0110 Vi\u1ec7t Nam VFF b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m \u00f4ng Jurgen Gede l\u00e0m G\u0110KT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 6/2016 theo b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 2 n\u0103m. B\u1eb1ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, v\u1ecb chuy\u00ean gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng vai ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng th\u1ea7m l\u1eb7ng trong c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1ebb trong th\u1eddi gian v\u1eeba qua.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong su\u1ed1t hai n\u0103m qua, G\u0110KT Jurgen Gede \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 tham d\u1ef1 &nbsp;VCK U20 World Cup, U15 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U15 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 danh hi\u1ec7u \u00c1 qu\u00e2n VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 c\u00f9ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap \u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn t\u1eeb c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a VFF. V\u00e0 sau 2 n\u0103m l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c, \u00f4ng Gede \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c VFF gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng khi b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng Gede v\u00e0 VFF s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n trong th\u00e1ng 7 n\u00e0y. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, sau khi \u00f4ng Gede tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 c\u00f9ng U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1, c\u1ea3 hai b\u00ean s\u1ebd ng\u1ed3i l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n th\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ea3o tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c &ldquo;ch\u1ed1t&rdquo; h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. B\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi gi\u1eefa G\u0110KT Gede v\u00e0 VFF d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd k\u00e9o d\u00e0i th\u00eam 2 n\u0103m. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, G\u0110KT Gede s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh c\u00f9ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch l\u1edbn trong 2 n\u0103m t\u1edbi. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn ASIAD 2018, AFF Cup 2018 v\u00e0 VCK Asian Cup 2019.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;&#10;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1219","checkdouble":"191108"},{"date":"15:55 13/07","title":"N\u00f3ng: \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c mua \u0111\u1ee9t \u2018Messi Th\u00e1i Lan\u2019","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/3/nong-doi-bong-nhat-ban-chinh-thuc-mua-dut-messi-thai-lan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u1ecb thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c b\u1edfi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Chanathip Songkrasin, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n Consadole Sapporo \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh mua \u0111\u1ee9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.\r\n\r\n</h2><h2><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Consadole Sapporo&nbsp;</span>ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c mua \u0111\u1ee9t Chanathip Songkrasin</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Chanathip Songkrasin t\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho CLB Consadole Sapporo t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 7/2017 theo m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n k\u00e9o d\u00e0i 1 n\u0103m r\u01b0\u1ee1i.&nbsp;T\u1ea1i x\u1ee9 s\u1edf Hoa anh \u0111\u00e0o, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 &lsquo;Messi Jay&rsquo; \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"N\u00f3ng \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c mua \u0111\u1ee9t Chanathip Songkrasin h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"N\u00f3ng \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c mua \u0111\u1ee9t Chanathip Songkrasin h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/3/them-cau-thu-thai-lan-ghi-ban-o-giai-jleague-1-nhat-ban.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Chanathip ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Consadole Sapporo</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau 1 n\u0103m thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i J1 League, Chanathip \u0111\u00e3 th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0&nbsp;ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 3 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n trong 14 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho&nbsp;Consadole&nbsp;\u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y gi\u1eefa Consadole Sapporo v\u1edbi Consadole Sapporo, Chanathip ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00e0 1 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n, g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n gi\u00fap Consadole v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0110N\u00c1 n\u00e0y, ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh mua \u0111\u1ee9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y t\u1eeb Muangthong United. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 song ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Muangthong United s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 thu v\u1ec1 kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n 570 ngh\u00ecn USD (13,1 t\u1ec9&nbsp;\u0111\u1ed3ng) t\u1eeb b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n Chanathip. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Consadole Sapporo mua \u0111\u1ee9t, Chanathip \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t CLB \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i J-League 1. \u0110\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 l\u1edbn h\u01a1n trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1218","checkdouble":"191109"},{"date":"16:01 13/07","title":"3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu HLV Sarri d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea thay Conte","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/13/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-4-nguoi-that-bai-neu-hlv-sarri-dan-dat-chelsea-thay-conte.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Maurizio Sarri t\u1edbi Chelsea thay Conte ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian, d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Andreas Christensen</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, Napoli l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t t\u1ee9 3 Serie A (sau Juventus v\u00e0 Roma), h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn 29 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 38 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 58 tu\u1ed5i lu\u00f4n \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng gi\u1eefa t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Maurizio Sarri t\u1edbi Chelsea thay Conte h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Maurizio Sarri t\u1edbi Chelsea thay Conte h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/HLV-Maurizio-Sarri-toi-Chelsea-thay-Conte-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Andreas Christensen nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Sarri tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Sarri c\u00f3 t\u01b0 duy b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 kh\u00e1 gi\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi Pep Guardiola, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n b\u00f3ng ngay t\u1eeb b\u00ean ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. \u1ede Napoli, Kalidou Koulibaly l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m vai tr\u00f2 n\u00e0y. Trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Senegal chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c c\u1ee7a anh l\u00ean t\u1edbi 95% \u1edf Serie A 2017/18.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede Stamford Bridge, trung v\u1ec7 Andreas Christensen c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Conte s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChristensen c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t, m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1996 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 93,4%, anh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 t\u1ea7m v\u00f3c t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i gi\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi Koulibaly. N\u1ebfu HLV Maurizio Sarri t\u1edbi Chelsea, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Christensen s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Manchester City</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man City l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean h\u1ecfi mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho c\u1ee7a Napoli, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad \u0111\u00e3 2 l\u1ea7n tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i. Theo \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00e0 35 v\u00e0 44 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, song \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu HLV Sarri d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea thay Conte h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu HLV Sarri d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea thay Conte h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-neu-HLV-Sarri-dan-dat-Chelsea-thay-Conte-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sarri gi\u00fap Chelsea mua Jorginho</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1eeda xanh th\u00e0nh Manchester g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb th\u1ee9 3 b\u1edfi Jorginho \u0111ang \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n Chelsea. B\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Anh \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f3 2 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Chelsea v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Man City trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Th\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1ee7 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0 Napoli y\u00eau c\u1ea7u, th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn The Blues theo ti\u1ebfng g\u1ecdi c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y c\u0169 Sarri.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea s\u1ebd c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 &ldquo;bom t\u1ea5n&rdquo; Jorginho c\u00f9ng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m ra m\u1eaft HLV Sarri. Theo ESPN, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London s\u1ebd ra m\u1eaft HLV Sarri v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Eden Hazard</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus, nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Real Madrid l\u00e0 t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf. Vi\u1ec7c Neymar v\u00e0 Mbappe c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn khi\u1ebfn Los Blancos d\u1ed3n to\u00e0n l\u1ef1c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Eden Hazard c\u1ee7a Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sarri muon bien Hazard thanh trung tam trong loi choi cua Chelsea\" title=\"Sarri mu\u1ed1n bi\u1ebfn Hazard th\u00e0nh trung t\u00e2m trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/ha.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sarri mu\u1ed1n bi\u1ebfn Hazard th\u00e0nh trung t\u00e2m trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00f4m nay, Daily Mail kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Real ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Hazard, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 27 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn NHM Chelsea lo l\u1eafng khi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 Real c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n. HLV Sarri d\u00f9 ch\u01b0a ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Chelsea song mu\u1ed1n BL\u0110 The Blues gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u1edf l\u1ea1i b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV 58 tu\u1ed5i d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea quanh Hazard, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 400.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Hazard \u1edf l\u1ea1i, t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a anh v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a The Blues \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng ch\u00fa \u00fd t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Antonio Conte</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Conte l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho Chelsea trong 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i qu\u00e1 t\u1ec7, theo \u0111\u00f3 m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u mang v\u1ec1 cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge \u00edt nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t danh hi\u1ec7u.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea thay conte sarri\" title=\"Chelsea thay conte sarri\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/John-Terry-phat-bieu-ve-Antonio-Conte-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Conte b\u1ecb Chelsea th\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7y cay \u0111\u1eafng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch m\u00e0 Conte \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 48 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu chung s\u1ed1 ph\u1eadn v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u HLV tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee7a Chelsea.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Chelsea gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a t\u1edbi, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-137-conte-da-bi-chelsea-sa-thai-421-191062.html\" target=\"_blank\">HLV Conte \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i</span>. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia th\u1ee9 9 m\u1ea5t vi\u1ec7c \u1edf Chelsea d\u01b0\u1edbi k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 Abramovich.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAn \u1ee7i l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi Conte l\u00e0 \u00f4ng s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec1n b\u00f9 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Chelsea. T\u00ednh c\u1ea3 c\u1ef1u HLV Juventus, The Blues \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec1n b\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho c\u00e1c HLV.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Ruben Loftus-Cheek</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 chi qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n trong 2 k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, b\u1edfi v\u1eady h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng mua s\u1eafm qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 HLV Sarri s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111ang c\u00f3 trong tay.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ruben Loftus-Cheek\" title=\"Ruben Loftus-Cheek\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/16/Thay-gi-sau-vu-tien-ve-Ross-Barkley-toi-Chelsea-hinh-anh-5.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ruben Loftus-Cheek \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Sarri s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i g\u1ecdi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, trong s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y Ruben Loftus-Cheek l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t. Ng\u00f4i sao 22 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Crystal Palace.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLoftus-Cheek th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0110T Anh, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1996 c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Gareth Southgate trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, n\u1ebfu Sarri c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Alvaro Morata</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Alvaro Morata \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb Real Madrid, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc nh\u1eefng g\u00ec anh th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. Ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cho Diego Costa \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Morata\" title=\"Morata\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/22/4-doi-bong-lon-san-sang-chi-60-trieu-euro-mua-bom-xit-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Morata s\u1eafp b\u1eadt b\u00e3i kh\u1ecfi Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i Morata ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 11 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1993 t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u cao nh\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh. C\u1ef1u sao Real li\u00ean t\u1ee5c d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, anh b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ngon \u0103n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00f2n tranh ch\u1ea5p r\u1ea5t k\u00e9m, ch\u00ednh m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Chelsea kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Sarri \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o nh\u01b0 Morata, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n Chelsea \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Dries Mertens c\u1ee7a Napoli ho\u1eb7c Gonzalo Higuain c\u1ee7a Juventus \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Conte t\u1ea1i v\u1ecb Morata c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao th\u00eam c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh, song khi m\u00e0 \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 48 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i c\u00f2n Sarri s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m, th\u1eddi gian c\u1ee7a Morata \u1edf Stamford Bridge ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n t\u00ednh b\u1eb1ng ng\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n*Squawka.com</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1217","checkdouble":"191110"},{"date":"16:35 13/07","title":"Real mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 v\u1ec1 thay Ronaldo","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/13/real-muon-mua-rodrigo-ve-thay-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real mu\u1ed1n mua Rodrigo v\u1ec1 thay Ronaldo, ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi sang Juventus. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 27 tu\u1ed5i t\u1eebng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb Los Blancos trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Real r\u00e1o ri\u1ebft t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay Ronaldo</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Cristiano Ronaldo ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro. Vi\u1ec7c CR7 mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n t\u1eeb l\u00e2u v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd anh m\u1edbi t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p. Ngo\u00e0i ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3, Juve c\u0169ng d\u00e0nh cho Ronaldo m\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3i ng\u1ed9 ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng c\u00f3 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 khi \u1edf Real.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n Real, h\u1ecd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 Ronaldo ra \u0111i khi ch\u01b0a t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, h\u1ecd c\u00f2n c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 m\u1ea5t n\u1ed1t Gareth Bale. Sau chung k\u1ebft Champions League, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 x\u1ee9 Wales \u0111\u00e3 b\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n s\u1ebd chia tay s\u00e2n Santiago Bernabeu n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real mu\u1ed1n mua Rodrigo v\u1ec1 thay Ronaldo, ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi sang Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real mu\u1ed1n mua Rodrigo v\u1ec1 thay Ronaldo, ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi sang Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/Real-muon-mua-Rodrigo-ve-thay-Ronaldo,-nguoi-moi-sang-Juventus-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 t\u1edbi Jvuentus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, M.U t\u00ednh \u0111\u01b0a Bale v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Old Trafford. C\u00f2n Real, h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao nh\u01b0 Neymar, Kylian Mbappe r\u1ed3i Eden Hazard v\u1ec1 c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Rodrigo l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm Real</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean tr\u00ean kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, Real mu\u1ed1n mua Rodrigo c\u1ee7a Valencia v\u1ec1 thay Ronaldo. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t kh\u00f4ng xa l\u1ea1 g\u00ec v\u1edbi Los Blancos v\u00e0 t\u00e2n HLV Julen Lopetegui c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien dao Rodrigo\" title=\"tien dao Rodrigo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/real-muon-mua-rodrigo-ve-thay-ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Real mu\u1ed1n mua Rodrigo c\u1ee7a Valencia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nRodrigo t\u1eebng t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb Real m\u00f9a 2009/10 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi sang Benfica r\u1ed3i t\u1edbi Valencia nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7n nay. V\u1edbi HLV Lopetegui, \u00f4ng t\u1eebng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Rodrigo tr\u00ean \u0110T U21 T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng nhau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u n\u0103m 2013.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1 \u0111a n\u0103ng khi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i c\u1ea3 trung phong l\u1eabn d\u1ea1t c\u00e1nh. D\u00f9 thay th\u1ebf Ronaldo hay Bale, Rodrigo \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 27 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft v\u1edbi Nacho, Dani Carvajal v\u00e0 Isco, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh \u1edf c\u00e1c l\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/mu-day-manh-qua-trinh-mua-gareth-bale-180-191077.html\">M.U \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 &ldquo;sao b\u1ef1&rdquo; Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/cuu-sao-real-danh-gia-cao-ronaldo-hon-hazard-neymar-187-191072.html\">C\u1ef1u sao Real \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Ronaldo h\u01a1n Hazard, Neymar</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-san-sang-chi-150-trieu-bang-de-mua-hazard-180-191070.html\">Real s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi gi\u00e1 cao kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ec3 mua Hazard</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-thua-nuoc-duc-tha-cau-vu-ronaldo-toi-juventus-172-191026.html\">Liverpool th\u1eeba n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ee5c th\u1ea3 c\u00e2u v\u1ee5 Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-muon-mua-hazard-cua-chelsea-180-191016.html\">Barca l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u1eabng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Real</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1216","checkdouble":"191111"},{"date":"17:45 13/07","title":"Modric: \"T\u00f4i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed5i 4 c\u00fap C1 \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/modric-toi-san-sang-doi-3-cup-c1-de-vo-dich-world-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Modric kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup s\u1eafp t\u1edbi v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi anh. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia c\u00f2n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1ecdi danh hi\u1ec7u Champions League t\u1eebng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p.</h2><h2>Modric quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Ph\u00e1p</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Croatia \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng chung k\u1ebft sau khi v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0110an M\u1ea1ch, Nga v\u00e0 Anh \u1edf v\u00f2ng knock-out. \u1ede c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Vatreni \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i nh\u1edd t\u1edbi hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang penalty m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ch\u00f4ng gai tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ti\u1ebfn t\u1edbi tr\u1ead chung k\u1ebft. V\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Luka Modric m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean d\u00e2y c\u00f3t cho \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng hai trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Modric quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u1edf chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Modric quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u1edf chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/Modric-quyet-tam-lam-nen-lich-su-o-chung-ket-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Modric quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u00f9ng Croatia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed5i 4 danh hi\u1ec7u Champions League m\u00ecnh t\u1eebng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea5y chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng World Cup. Kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed th\u1ec3 thao Croatia. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f2n h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau cao h\u01a1n l\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin, tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 m\u1ecdi y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 m\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Modric kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Modric c\u0169ng \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng \u1edf k\u1ef3 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span>. Tuy v\u1eady, anh t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n m\u00e0 t\u1eadp trung nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n v\u00e0o th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a t\u1eadp th\u1ec3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u h\u1ecfi t\u00f4i v\u1ec1 danh hi\u1ec7u Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb \u00e1p l\u1ef1c b\u1edfi n\u00f3. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup n\u0103m nay b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cKhi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00e1 khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng. Nh\u01b0ng d\u1ea7n d\u1ea7n, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t ni\u1ec1m tin m\u00e0 ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3. V\u00e0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd th\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft l\u1ecbch s\u1eed\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Ph\u00e1p:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/chung-ket-world-cup-2018-4-ly-do-de-tin-dt-phap-se-vo-dich-421-191099.html\">Chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018: 4 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin \u0110T Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/quy-luat-20-nam-se-giup-croatia-viet-nen-doan-ket-co-tich-421-191097.html\">Quy lu\u1eadt 20 n\u0103m s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Croatia vi\u1ebft n\u00ean \u0111o\u1ea1n k\u1ebft c\u1ed5 t\u00edch</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1215","checkdouble":"191113"},{"date":"16:58 13/07","title":"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i HLV Antonio Conte","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/13/chinh-thuc-chelsea-sa-thai-hlv-antonio-conte.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c sa th\u1ea3i HLV Antonio Conte \u0111\u1ec3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 d\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cho m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia kh\u00e1c t\u1edbi Stamford Bridge trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.</h2><h2>Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i HLV Antonio Conte<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div>Sau nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n, vi\u1ec7c Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i HLV Antonio Conte \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt. Trang ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Chelsea x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn v\u1edbi th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o: &quot;Trong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian Antonio Conte \u1edf c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9, ch\u00fang ta gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 6 v\u00e0 FA Cup l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 8&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea sa thai HLV Antonio Conte truoc them mua giai moi.\" title=\"Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i HLV Antonio Conte tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/chinh-thuc-chelsea-sa-thai-hlv-antonio-conte.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i HLV Antonio Conte tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&quot;Trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ea1t k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c 30 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong 38 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i Premier League, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 v\u1edbi 13 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mong Antonio Conte lu\u00f4n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>T\u1eeb giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Chelsea thi \u0111\u1ea5u thi\u1ebfu \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c HLV Antonio Conte b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n. HLV Conte \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00f2ng c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t do nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sai l\u1ea7m trong vi\u1ec7c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c ru\u1ed3ng r\u1eaby Diego Costa.<br>\r\n<h2>Ai s\u1ebd thay th\u1ebf Conte?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Anh \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd ng\u1ed3i v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf  n\u00f3ng \u1edf Stamford Bridge sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Conte l\u00e0 Maurizio Sarri. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3,  Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 chi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec1n b\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho Napoli \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 59  tu\u1ed5i.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1edf d\u0129 HLV Sarri ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ebfn Chelsea b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Napoli.  Trong ba m\u00f9a d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Napoli, HLV Sarri d\u00f9 ch\u01b0a gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Naples gi\u00e0nh  scudetto nh\u01b0ng tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ea7y h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng n\u00e2ng t\u1ea7m c\u1ea7u  th\u1ee7.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ea9y Antonio Conte ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia m\u1edbi \u1edf th\u1eddi  \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn c\u1ee7a Chelsea. Khi World Cup 2018 k\u1ebft  th\u00fac, c\u00e1c HLV s\u1ebd t\u00ecm ra nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 nh\u1eb1m chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho  m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 HLV Antonio Conte:</h2>\r\n<div><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-4-nguoi-that-bai-neu-hlv-sarri-dan-dat-chelsea-thay-conte-172-191110.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu HLV Sarri d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea thay Conte</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/john-terry-noi-gi-sau-khi-chelsea-sa-thai-conte-172-191101.html\">John Terry n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i Conte?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-nhin-chelsea-quyet-dinh-thay-the-conte-bang-sarri-172-191093.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Sarri quy\u1ebfn r\u0169 \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2u \u0111\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn Chelsea &ldquo;ph\u1ee5 t\u00ecnh&rdquo; Conte?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tu-biet-conte-sao-chelsea-khong-quen-trach-moc-mot-chuyen-172-191091.html\">T\u1eeb bi\u1ec7t Conte, sao Chelsea kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean tr\u00e1ch m\u00f3c m\u1ed9t chuy\u1ec7n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-137-conte-da-bi-chelsea-sa-thai-421-191062.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 13/7: Conte \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/vu-hlv-sarri-den-chelsea-co-dien-bien-moi-172-191036.html\">V\u1ee5 HLV Sarri \u0111\u1ebfn Chelsea c\u00f3 di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1214","checkdouble":"191114"},{"date":"17:08 13/07","title":"Croatia tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Ph\u00e1p: Tinh th\u1ea7n c\u00f3 kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/12/croatia-truoc-tran-gap-phap-tinh-than-co-khoa-lap-yeu-to-the-luc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Croatia \u0111\u00e3 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup, tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i d\u00f9ng tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00e1p v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi Croatia v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Croatia \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t \u1edf World Cup 2018, 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 th\u00eam gi\u1edd. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3&nbsp;th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u c\u00e2n n\u00e3o.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia Tinh th\u1ea7n c\u00f3 kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia Tinh th\u1ea7n c\u00f3 kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/Phap-vs-Croatia-Tinh-than-co-khoa-lap-yeu-to-the-luc-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Croatia l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u ph\u00fat nh\u1ea5t \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi Anh \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n t\u1edbi lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u00e1 11m nh\u01b0ng Croatia \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3i qua 120 ph\u00fat m\u1ec7t nho\u00e0i m\u1edbi b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1. T\u00ednh t\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Dalic \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 675 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft th\u00ec Croatia \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n 95 ph\u00fat, t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCroatia \u0111\u00e3 v\u1eaft ki\u1ec7t s\u1ee9c \u1edf 3 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua th\u00ec Ph\u00e1p l\u1ea1i ch\u01b0a m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 qua c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 th\u00eam gi\u1edd. T\u1ed5ng th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Les Bleus \u1edf World Cup 2018 l\u00e0 580 ph\u00fat.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n2 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uruguay v\u00e0 B\u1ec9, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Didier Deschamps nh\u1edd chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt h\u1ee3p l\u00fd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5t qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ee9c l\u1ef1c, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t n\u00e0o v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hay th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ed1ng k\u00ea ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u1ec1 qu\u00e3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng di chuy\u1ec3n \u1edf World Cup 2018 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang do Croatia n\u1eafm gi\u1eef. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Luka Modric l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi di chuy\u1ec3n nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi 63,2 km, Marcelo Brozovic l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 di chuy\u1ec3n nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Modric kiet suc sau tran ban ket voi Anh\" title=\"Modric ki\u1ec7t s\u1ee9c sau tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Anh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/modric.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Modric ki\u1ec7t s\u1ee9c sau tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Anh, Brozovic \u0111\u00e3 di chuy\u1ec3n qu\u00e3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 16,4 km. Vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3i qua 3 m\u00e0n tra t\u1ea5n th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp khi\u1ebfn th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Croatia ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd b\u1ecb b\u00e0o m\u00f2n \u0111i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c v\u1edbi Anh, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Croatia li\u00ean t\u1ee5c n\u1eb1m s\u00e2n v\u00ec m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd nh\u01b0 Modric v\u00e0 Mandukic \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u00edt th\u1eddi gian h\u01a1n m\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 1 ng\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u0169ng tr\u1ebb trung h\u01a1n Croatia r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Phap vuot troi so voi Croatia ve mat the luc\" title=\"Ph\u00e1p v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi Croatia v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/phap.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ph\u00e1p v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi Croatia v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong s\u1ed1 11 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p v\u01b0\u1ee3t qu\u00e1 tu\u1ed5i 30, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Hugo Lloris, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Blaise Matuidi v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Olivier Giroud. Ph\u00e1p s\u1edf h\u1eefu r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111ang \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i sung s\u1ee9c nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKylian Mbappe (20 tu\u1ed5i), Benjamin Pavard (22 tu\u1ed5i), Lucas Hernandez (22 tu\u1ed5i), Samuel Umtiti (24 tu\u1ed5i)... \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 sung s\u1ee9c h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u00f4ng gi\u00e0 nay c\u00f2n b\u1ecb b\u00e0o m\u00f2n s\u1ee9c l\u1ef1c b\u00ean ph\u00eda Croatia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Tinh th\u1ea7n c\u00f3 gi\u00fap Croatia l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p?</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/chung-ket-world-cup-2018-4-ly-do-de-tin-dt-phap-se-vo-dich-421-191099.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia</span>, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Dalic b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u1ec1 c\u1ea3 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 m\u1eb7t th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c, tinh th\u1ea7n l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 duy nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc Les Bleus.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Croatia an mung ban go 1-1\" title=\"Croatia \u0103n m\u1eebng b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 1-1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/thong-ke-gay-soc-sau-that-bai-cua-anh-truoc-croatia.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>S\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh tinh th\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Croatia \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Ph\u00e1p</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede World Cup 2018, Croatia \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Trong 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch, Nga v\u00e0 Anh \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u1eabn b\u00e0n nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. \u1ede tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Anh, Strinic 3 l\u1ea7n n\u1eb1m s\u00e2n v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean y t\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u0169ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Luzhniki, Mandzukic hay Modric \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecb \u0111au v\u00e0 ki\u1ec7t s\u1ee9c nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eadn nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5 th\u1ee9 2. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u00fd ch\u00ed ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1edbi gi\u00fap h\u1ecd l\u00e0m n\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u th\u1ea7n k\u1ef3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ee9c tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Anh trong 120 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u.&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Croatia \u1edf tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ivan-perisic-tiet-lo-ly-do-giup-croatia-co-the-danh-bai-phap-421-191086.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ivan Perisic</span> kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft v\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 tinh th\u1ea7n s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Les Bleus \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;3 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 th\u00eam 3 gi\u1edd, 3 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp b\u1ecb d\u1eabn b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1u v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua. Tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Croatia, t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng tinh th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Croatia l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1edd b\u00f3ng l\u0103n, m\u1ecdi \u01b0u th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec1u nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda \u0110T Ph\u00e1p. Ch\u00fat l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf \u00edt \u1ecfi m\u00e0 Croatia \u0111ang n\u1eafm trong tay l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 tinh th\u1ea7n. Nh\u01b0ng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh gi\u00fap h\u1ecd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t c\u01a1n \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0o Ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1213","checkdouble":"191115"},{"date":"10:27 13/07","title":"Ivan Perisic ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Croatia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Ph\u00e1p","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/ivan-perisic-tiet-lo-ly-do-giup-croatia-co-the-danh-bai-phap.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ivan Perisic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Inter Milan ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Les Bleus trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Croatia l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCroatia kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao \u1edf World Cup 2018, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c cao. Luka Modric t\u1ea1o ra c\u00fa s\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Argentina 3-0 \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ivan Perisic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ivan Perisic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/Ivan-Perisic-phat-bieu-ve-tran-Phap-vs-Croatia-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110T Croatia l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng do HLV Dalic d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u0169ng g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D, b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Argentina. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, Croatia \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ecb d\u1eabn b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd v\u1eabn ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ee1 v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u00e1 lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u c\u00e2n n\u00e3o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Anh, Croatia th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi ngay t\u1eeb ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 5. Tuy nhi\u00ean, b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u00f9ng s\u1ef1 kinh nghi\u1ec7m gi\u00fap h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t c\u00fa ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng kinh \u0111i\u1ec3n v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 sau 120 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-croatia-vs-anh-421-190986.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Croatia vs Anh </span>gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Ph\u00e1p \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ec9 kho\u1ea3ng 4 tri\u1ec7u d\u00e2n nh\u01b0 Croatia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Perisic ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c gi\u00fap Croatia \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Ph\u00e1p</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ivan Perisic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Inter Milan ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Les Bleus trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Perisic\" title=\"Perisic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/mourinho-tiet-lo-ly-do-muon-dua-perisic-ve-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Perisic quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m b\u00e1o th\u00f9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cN\u0103m 1998, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i thua Ph\u00e1p 1-2 \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n Croatia b\u00e2y gi\u1edd v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t cay \u0111\u1eafng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Ph\u00e1p, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng b\u00e1o th\u00f9. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n mang l\u1ea1i ni\u1ec1m vui cho NHM\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201c3 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 th\u00eam 3 gi\u1edd, 3 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp b\u1ecb d\u1eabn b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1u v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua. Tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Croatia, t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng tinh th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Croatia l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1212","checkdouble":"191086"},{"date":"10:05 13/07","title":"H\u00e9 l\u1ed9 c\u00e1i t\u00ean th\u1ee9 hai ph\u1ea3i chia tay M.U trong 48 gi\u1edd t\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/14/he-lo-cai-ten-thu-hai-phai-chia-tay-mu-trong-48-gio-toi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Anh m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 h\u00e9 l\u1ed9 v\u1ec1 c\u00e1i t\u00ean th\u1ee9 hai s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chia tay CLB Man Utd trong v\u00f2ng 48 gi\u1edd t\u1edbi.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify; \">M.U chia tay&nbsp;Daley Blind</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Daley Blind\" title=\"Daley Blind\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/15/ajax-chi-mua-lai-daley-blind-voi-mot-dieu-kien.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>M.U chia tay Daley Blind trong 48 gi\u1edd t\u1edbi</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao b\u1ecb th\u1ea5t s\u1ee7ng t\u1ea1i M.U d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Mourinho khi lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn th\u1ee9 y\u1ebfu \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 sau nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 Chris Smalling, Phil Jones, Eric Bailly v\u00e0 Victor Lindelof, ng\u00e0y chia tay M.U c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Daley Blind \u0111ang t\u1edbi r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 khi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u1eeba chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i m\u1edbi 19 tu\u1ed5i Diogo Dalot t\u1eeb Porto.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Mirror d\u1eabn ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb De Telegraaf c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 Lan x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn, Daley Blind \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi Ajax v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t trong v\u00f2ng 48 gi\u1edd t\u1edbi. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Blind kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n v\u1ec1 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford khi ch\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00fang 7 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i Premier League. V\u00ec l\u00fd do \u0111\u00f3 anh \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i v\u00e0 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a Ajax. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Ajax r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Blind tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i H\u00e0 Lan s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1edfi h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i Champions League s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 25/7 t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t trong 48 ti\u1ebfng t\u1edbi, Daley Blind s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean th\u1ee9 2 \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i 1 chia tay Man United trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc anh,&nbsp;th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Sam Johnstone \u0111\u00e3&nbsp;chia tay M.U \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n sang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o West Brom v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/mu-day-manh-qua-trinh-mua-gareth-bale-180-191077.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/1/gareth-bale-duoc-khuyen-bo-real-ve-voi-mu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/mu-day-manh-qua-trinh-mua-gareth-bale-180-191077.html\">M.U \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 &ldquo;sao b\u1ef1&rdquo; Real</span><br>\r\nSau khi m\u1ea5t \u0111i Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0o tay Juventus, Real Madrid l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n v\u1edbi n\u1ed7i lo m\u1ea5t th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao n\u1eefa. Th\u00f4ng tin MU \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh mua Gareth...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-127-mu-theo-duoi-1-chang-cristiano-khac-cua-sporting-184-191057.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-127-mu-theo-duoi-1-chang-cristiano-khac-cua-sporting.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-127-mu-theo-duoi-1-chang-cristiano-khac-cua-sporting-184-191057.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 12/7: MU theo \u0111u\u1ed5i 1 ch\u00e0ng Cristiano kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Sporting</span><br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 12/7.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-tiet-lo-ly-do-muon-dua-perisic-ve-mu-172-191059.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/mourinho-tiet-lo-ly-do-muon-dua-perisic-ve-mu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-tiet-lo-ly-do-muon-dua-perisic-ve-mu-172-191059.html\">Mourinho khen ng\u1ee3i m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau MU sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Anh</span><br>\r\nHLV Jose Mourinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Ivan Perisic t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford sau khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ghi b\u00e0n khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u00f4m h\u1eadn.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1211","checkdouble":"191087"},{"date":"10:17 13/07","title":"Sao Roma kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi Ronaldo c\u1ee7a Juventus","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/kevin-strootman-khong-ngai-doi-dau-ronaldo-tai-serie-a.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Cesc Fabregas cho r\u1eb1ng ch\u00ednh th\u1eddi gian kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn anh \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u1edf World Cup 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-137-conte-da-bi-chelsea-sa-thai-421-191062.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i Conte</span> ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian s\u1edbm mu\u1ed9n b\u1edfi tin t\u1ee9c n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n b\u00e1o uy t\u00ednh x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn. V\u00e0 r\u1ed3i ngay c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong cu\u1ed9c nh\u01b0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Cesc Fabregas \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng th\u00ec ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f2n g\u00ec nghi ng\u1edd n\u1eefa.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i Conte, Fabregas t\u1ea1m bi\u1ec7t v\u00e0 tr\u00e1ch c\u1ee9 th\u1ea7y c\u0169 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i Conte, Fabregas t\u1ea1m bi\u1ec7t v\u00e0 tr\u00e1ch c\u1ee9 th\u1ea7y c\u0169 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/tu-biet-conte-sao-chelsea-khong-quen-trach-moc-mot-chuyen.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Fabregas l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng sau khi Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i Conte</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 31 tu\u1ed5i tr\u00ean trang Twitter c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n: \u201cC\u1ea3m \u01a1n th\u1ea7y v\u00ec nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u Premier League v\u00e0 FA Cup. Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng g\u00ec cho t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n trong m\u1eaft th\u1ea7y nh\u01b0ng sau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn th\u1ea7y c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o. Ch\u00fac th\u1ea7y m\u1ecdi s\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e2y, Fabregas c\u0169ng c\u00f3 \u00fd tr\u00e1ch c\u1ee9 Conte kh\u00f4ng tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng anh trong m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u1edf World Cup 2018. C\u1ef1u th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Arsenal n\u00f3i th\u00eam:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng khi Conte m\u1edbi l\u00ean n\u1eafm quy\u1ec1n \u1edf Chelsea, c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Julen Lopetegui \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m l\u00e0m HLV T\u00e2y Ban Nha. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 v\u00ec th\u1ebf m\u00e0 t\u00f4i m\u1edbi ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i nh\u00e0 \u1edf World Cup 2018, khi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1ee9a U19 v\u00e0 U21 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng h\u01a1n. Th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 th\u00ec h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t trong su\u1ed1t hai n\u0103m qua.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u1eeb bi\u1ec7t Conte, Fabregas chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00f3n th\u1ea7y m\u1edbi c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u1ef1u HLV Maurizio Sarri c\u1ee7a Napoli.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-bo-nhiem-sarri-chuong-su-moi-voi-ga-nhan-vien-ngan-hang-172-187380.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/30/chelsea-bo-nhiem-sarri-thu-thach-long-kien-nhan-voi-ga-nhan-vien-ngan-hang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-bo-nhiem-sarri-chuong-su-moi-voi-ga-nhan-vien-ngan-hang-172-187380.html\">Chelsea b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Sarri: Ch\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1eed m\u1edbi v\u1edbi g\u00e3 nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng</span><br>\r\nChelsea b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Sarri thay th\u1ebf HLV Conte trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cao v\u00e0 qua \u0111\u00e2y, Stamford Bridge s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i, k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1210","checkdouble":"191088"},{"date":"10:53 13/07","title":"MU ch\u1ed1t 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua trung v\u1ec7 tuy\u1ec3n Anh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/mu-chot-50-trieu-bang-mua-trung-ve-tuyen-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>MU mu\u1ed1n mua Harry Maguire c\u1ee7a Leicester, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mourinho mu\u1ed1n MU mua Maguire</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede World Cup 2018, Harry Maguire l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1993 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 m\u00e0 anh c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u1edf kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU mu\u1ed1n mua Harry Maguire c\u1ee7a Leicester v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU mu\u1ed1n mua Harry Maguire c\u1ee7a Leicester v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/mu-chot-50-trieu-bang-mua-trung-ve-tuyen-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Harry Maguire g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi Mourinho</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ghi 1 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 1 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o sau 5 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf World Cup 2018. Phong c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh khi\u1ebfn Mourinho \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMU mu\u1ed1n mua Harry Maguire c\u1ee7a Leicester, HLV Mourinho \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Old Trafford.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua Maguire c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Leicester, anh ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ee7 38 tr\u1eadn \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, ghi 2 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 4 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. C\u1ea7u&nbsp;th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/man-city-chi-50-trieu-bang-mua-trung-ve-cua-leicester-172-177232.html\" target=\"_blank\">Man City c\u0169ng h\u1ecfi mua Maguire </span>song Leicester \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 bu\u1ed9c h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Lapore c\u1ee7a Bilbao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>MU ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Maguire</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Leicester b\u00e1n Maguire, MU ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n King Power kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh l\u00ean 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Harry Maguire\" title=\"Harry Maguire\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/Anh-vao-ban-ket-World-Cup-Lai-la-nguoi-hung-Harry,-nhung-khong-phai-nhu-ban-dang-nghi!-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Harry Maguire</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nLeicester ch\u1ec9 m\u1ea5t 17 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Maguire, n\u1ebfu b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i cho MU v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd l\u00e3i l\u1edbn trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean,&nbsp;&ldquo;B\u1ea7y c\u00e1o&rdquo; s\u1ebd l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 bu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford ph\u1ea3i chi th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMan City \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i r\u1ea5t v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mahrez, h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i chi t\u1edbi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i. M.U nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u0169ng s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Maguire \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i, Mourinho s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7. V\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m t\u1eebng thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh Maguire s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi M.U.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1209","checkdouble":"191089"},{"date":"11:56 13/07","title":"Chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018: \u0110\u00e3 r\u00f5 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/13/chung-ket-world-cup-2018-xac-dinh-trong-tai-bat-chinh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, danh t\u00ednh tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn vinh d\u1ef1 c\u1ea7m c\u00f2i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina, Nestor Pitana.</h2><h2>X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/13/Chung-ket-World-Cup-2018-Xac-dinh-trong-tai-bat-chinh--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Nestor Pitana \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5\u00a0b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 22h00 t\u1ed1i Ch\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt t\u1edbi. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u r\u1ea5t \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i gi\u1eefa m\u1ed9t b\u00ean l\u00e0 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd cho ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u00ean l\u00e0 \u0110T Croatia \u0111ang l\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1edd b\u00f3ng l\u0103n, danh t\u00ednh v\u1ecb vua \u00e1o \u0111en s\u1ebd \u2018c\u1ea7m c\u00e2n, n\u1ea3y m\u1ef1c\u2019 tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u quan tr\u1ecdng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina, Nestor Pitana.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng Pitana kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean qu\u00e1 xa l\u1ea1 t\u1ea1i World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y khi t\u1eebng b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh trong tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft gi\u1eefa Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 Uruguay. D\u00f9 b\u1ecb nghi ng\u1edd (khi Argentina v\u1eeba b\u1ecb Ph\u00e1p lo\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8) nh\u01b0ng \u201c\u00f4ng vua \u00e1o \u0111en\u201d n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh t\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f4ng t\u00e2m trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady, v\u1ecb vua \u00e1o \u0111en n\u00e0y c\u00f2n l\u00e0m r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Croatia v\u00e0 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu h\u00fat s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng gi\u1eefa Nga - Saudi Arabia v\u00e0 Mexico - Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Nestor Pitana nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a FIFA \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7m c\u00f2i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. Hai tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng Pitana s\u1ebd l\u00e0 hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Hernan Maidana v\u00e0 Juan Belatti.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:\n16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ivan-perisic-tiet-lo-ly-do-giup-croatia-co-the-danh-bai-phap-421-191086.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/ivan-perisic-tiet-lo-ly-do-giup-croatia-co-the-danh-bai-phap.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ivan-perisic-tiet-lo-ly-do-giup-croatia-co-the-danh-bai-phap-421-191086.html\">Ivan Perisic ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Croatia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Ph\u00e1p</span><br>\r\nIvan Perisic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Inter Milan ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Les Bleus trong tr\u1eadn chung...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/pogba-khong-dam-coi-thuong-croatia-421-191079.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/pogba-khong-dam-coi-thuong-croatia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/pogba-khong-dam-coi-thuong-croatia-421-191079.html\">Pogba n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Chung k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p \u0110T Croatia?</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng khi \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Croatia.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ket-thuc-chien-dich-world-cup-harry-kane-tran-tre-hy-vong-vao-tuong-lai-421-191067.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/ket-thuc-chien-dich-world-cup-harry-kane-tran-tre-hy-vong-vao-tuong-lai.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ket-thuc-chien-dich-world-cup-harry-kane-tran-tre-hy-vong-vao-tuong-lai-421-191067.html\">K\u1ebft th\u00fac chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup, Harry Kane tr\u00e0n tr\u1ec1 hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft nh\u01b0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u1ec1 ra, nh\u01b0ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Harry Kane tin t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u0110T Anh s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng sau gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</span></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1208","checkdouble":"191090"}]}